mRULER.  V2.1 This macro will give a virtual
ruler on the line below the current cursor
line.

Features:
*   Places ruler under line of interest.
*   Works when screen is horizontally
    scrolled.
*   Supports offset starting column.
*   Default offset column is cursor column.
*   User can shift screen while retaining
    ruler by cursoring, tabbing, rolling, and
    Home/End.
*   Allows user configured ruler attribute
